Fyi, primary implementation changes are in StreamProcessor.java, ProcessorIdGenerator.java, SamzaObjectMapper.java, JsonContainerModelMixin.java and JsonJobModelMixin.java. 
Everything else is a side-effect of changing processorId from int to String. 

Due to the large-scope of this change, I would prefer to get explicit approvals from folks owning certain components. I have listed them below. Please review the main classes listed above and the components listed under your name. Appreciate the extra pair of eyes to make sure I don't break existing behavior. 

@vjagadish1989 All classes related to YarnClusterResourceManager - AppMasterService, ApplicationMaster{Rest,Web}Servlet, ContainerAllocator, ContainerRunner etc. 

@jmakes All class related to TaskAssignmentManager, BalancingTaskNameGrouper implementation and tests.

@nickpan47 All classes :) 

Thanks a lot everyone!

@navina 

Please take a look when you get a chance.

Squashed commits into single commit with meaningful message.

@prateekm 

Added additional asserts to test metrics reporting through listener. 

Thanks.
